description: President Volodymyr Zelensky urged people to show solidarity and remember "we are all human".
title: Coronavirus: Ukraine protesters attack buses carrying China evacuees
title_page: Coronavirus: Ukraine protesters attack buses carrying China evacuees - BBC News
maintext: "But there is another danger that I would like to mention. The danger of forgetting that we are all human and we are all Ukrainians. Each of us - including those who ended up in Wuhan during the epidemic."
